name: The Raven's Winter Giclee Print 16"x20" or 18"x24"
description:
Title: "The Raven's Winter Perch"

This is an image from my “Butterbroda” series which juxtaposes beauty with decay and innocence with danger.

This image is drawn digitally and is digitally signed on the front, within the art. Both the 16”x20" and 18"x24" prints will have a white border.

I print from a fine art print service, which produces exceptional Giclee prints. The printer uses archival inks on a heavy fine art paper which is 100% cotton and acid free.

Shipping within US:
Prints will arrive directly from the printer by FedEx 3-day delivery. Shipping is factored into the price of the print. The printing and shipping time, combined, will be approximately 8-10 business days.

Shipping to UK and Canada:
My printer doesn't ship internationally, so first the prints will be shipped to me (within 8-10 business days) and then I will ship the prints to you, via USPS International Priority Mail. Prints will be rolled to provide added protection. USPS International Priority Mail will take 12+ days depending on distance and customs, but I'll provide the customs form # for tracking purposes.

**Please note: 
The watermark of my web address, and the stripe it sits on, will not appear on the final print.
The colors of the print will differ slightly from the colors of the image you see online.
